thread.title: Marie Cooney
thread.title_full: Maine Lobster Now reviewed by Marie Cooney

author: Marie Cooney
title: Marie Cooney
text: Eight pound and a half lobsters and little neck clams were sent to Arizona for Christmas eve! Everything arrived in perfect condition and on time. I loved playing head cook for the family reunion, as someone who has enjoyed lobsters from Maine, while growing up in New England! Everything was perfect! And the prices were far more reasonable than other sights I looked at on the internet. I am so happy that my sister, living in the Boston area, had delivered lobsters from you before and had very high expectations that I would be equally delighted!
